----------------------------------------------------------------------
GPL-3 derived components
----------------------------------------------------------------------

The following parts of jointCPUE contain modified code derived from GPL-3
licensed software.

VAST

Modified code fragments and structural patterns adapted from VAST are used in:

  src/jointCPUE.cpp
    spatiotemporal likelihood structure

  R/index.R
    bias-correction workflow

  R/extra-optimization.R
    multi-stage optimization pattern

The statistical model implemented in jointCPUE is different from VAST and
is designed for joint CPUE standardization.

sdmTMB

Modified helper workflows derived from sdmTMB are used in:

  R/make_mesh.R
    mesh construction workflow patterns

These implementations were adapted for the jointCPUE framework and are not
statistically equivalent to sdmTMB.

